fields.name: cert-config
fields.description: Stores standard x509 crypto data elements in '/etc/openstack/cert'

fields.name: compute-api-config
fields.description: Holds the configuration stored in '/etc/openstack/compute-api'

fields.name: configure-eth2
fields.description: Controls configuration for the VPX public network interface stored in /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth2

fields.name: dashboard-config
fields.description: Stores configuration for OpenStack Dashboard in '/etc/openstack/dashboard'

fields.name: ensure-glance-init-run
fields.description: Triggered for first-time provisioning of the Image Registry and API

fields.name: ensure-keystone-init-run
fields.description: Triggered for first-time provisioning of the OpenStack Keystone.

fields.name: ensure-mysql-init-run
fields.description: Triggered for first-time provisioning of the Compute Database

fields.name: ensure-nova-volume-init-run
fields.description: Triggered for first-time provisioning of the OpenStack Nova Volume

fields.name: ensure-openstack-dashboard-init-run
fields.description: Triggered for first-time provisioning of the OpenStack Dashboard

fields.name: ensure-swift-init-run
fields.description: Triggered for the attaching disks to Object Workers

fields.name: ensure-swift-ring-builder-init-run
fields.description: Triggered for the auto-generation of ring files

fields.name: geppetto-syslog-config
fields.description: Stores configuration for logging remotely in '/etc/openstack/syslog'.

fields.name: geppetto-vpx-config
fields.description: Stores VPX properties in '/etc/openstack/geppetto'. For VPX on XenServer these get shown in XenCenter too

fields.name: glance-config
fields.description: Stores properties to configure the Image Servers in '/etc/openstack/glance'

fields.name: glance-store-config
fields.description: Stores Glance backend configuration in '/etc/openstack/glance-store'

fields.name: hapi-config
fields.description: Stores credentials and elements to access the hypevisor in '/etc/openstack/hapi'

fields.name: keystone-config
fields.description: Stores all the configuration related to Keystone in '/etc/openstack/keystone'.

fields.name: memcached
fields.description: Internal use only

fields.name: mysql-config
fields.description: Stores credentials to access the database in '/etc/openstack/mysql'

fields.name: openstack-role-set
fields.description: Control configuration. Internal use only

fields.name: rabbitmq-config
fields.description: Stores credentials to access the message queue in '/etc/openstack/rabbitmq'

fields.name: scheduler-config
fields.description: The configuration for openstack-nova-scheduler

fields.name: swift-config
fields.description: Stores swift configuration elements in '/etc/openstack/swift'

fields.name: swift-disks-config
fields.description: Stores configuration elements for swift object servers in '/etc/openstack/swift-store'

fields.name: swift-rings-config
fields.description: Ring files dispatcher. Internal use only

fields.name: volume-config
fields.description: Stores properties to configure the OpenStack Nova Volume Service in '/etc/openstack/volume'

fields.name: API_BIND_HOST
fields.description: The interface on which Glance API should be listening

fields.name: API_BIND_PORT
fields.description: The port to be used for Glance API

fields.name: COMPUTE_API_HOST
fields.description: Holds the fqdn of the compute api

fields.name: CRED_CERT_C
fields.description: Country for the user certificate subject

fields.name: CRED_CERT_L
fields.description: City or Locality for the user certificate subject

fields.name: CRED_CERT_O
fields.description: Organization for the user certificate subject

fields.name: CRED_CERT_OU
fields.description: Organizational Unit for the user certificate subject

fields.name: CRED_CERT_ST
fields.description: State for the user certificate subject

fields.name: DASHBOARD_SMTP_PWD
fields.description: User password for mail notifications

fields.name: DASHBOARD_SMTP_SVR
fields.description: SMTP server for mail notifications

fields.name: DASHBOARD_SMTP_USR
fields.description: User account for mail notifications

fields.name: ETH2_HOST_NETWORK
fields.description: Network on which to connect the virtual interface to

fields.name: ETH2_IP
fields.description: Static IP address for the interface

fields.name: ETH2_MODE
fields.description: Configuration mode

fields.name: ETH2_NETMASK
fields.description: Netmask for the interface

fields.name: GLANCE_FILE_STORE_SIZE_GB
fields.description: 'file' backend only: the size of the disk that serves the filestore backend

fields.name: GLANCE_HOSTNAME
fields.description: FQDN for the VPX node on which Glance servers are running

fields.name: GLANCE_STORE
fields.description: The type of storage backend supported by Glance API

fields.name: GLANCE_SWIFT_ADDRESS
fields.description: 'swift' backend only: the fqdn of the Swift API server

fields.name: GLANCE_SWIFT_STORE_KEY
fields.description: 'swift' backend only: the store key for accessing glance images on swift

fields.name: GLANCE_SWIFT_USER
fields.description: 'swift' backend only: the {account,user} tuple to access glance images on swift

fields.name: HAPI_PASS
fields.description: The user password

fields.name: HAPI_USER
fields.description: The user name

fields.name: IQN_PREFIX
fields.description: Prefix for iscsi volumes

fields.name: ISCSI_IP_PREFIX
fields.description: Discover volumes on the ip that starts with this prefix

fields.name: KEYSTONE_HOST
fields.description: The FQDN of the keystone node.

fields.name: KEYSTONE_SUPERUSER_NAME
fields.description: The admin user provisioned automatically in Keystone.

fields.name: KEYSTONE_SUPERUSER_PASS
fields.description: The password for the user provisioned automatically in Keystone.

fields.name: KEYSTONE_SUPERUSER_TENANT
fields.description: The admin tenant provisioned automatically in Keystone.

fields.name: KEYSTONE_SUPERUSER_TOKEN
fields.description: The token for the admin user provisioned automatically in Keystone.

fields.name: MYSQL_DBS
fields.description: Comma separated list of DBs to be provided by this MySQL host.

fields.name: MYSQL_HOST
fields.description: The FQDN of the database node

fields.name: MYSQL_PASS
fields.description: The user password

fields.name: MYSQL_TYPE
fields.description: Mark if the database is not managed and provisioned by Geppetto. Internal use only

fields.name: MYSQL_USER
fields.description: The user name

fields.name: RABBIT_HOST
fields.description: The FQDN of the message queue node

fields.name: RABBIT_PASS
fields.description: The user password

fields.name: RABBIT_PORT
fields.description: The port on which RabbitMQ server is listening

fields.name: RABBIT_USER
fields.description: The user name

fields.name: REGISTRY_BIND_HOST
fields.description: The interface on which Glance Registry should be listening

fields.name: REGISTRY_BIND_PORT
fields.description: The port to be used for Glance Registry

fields.name: SCHEDULER_COMPUTE_DRIVER
fields.description: Specifies the scheduler that deals with the compute operations.

fields.name: SCHEDULER_DEFAULT_HOST_FILTER
fields.description: Specifies the host filter used by the scheduler.

fields.name: SCHEDULER_VOLUME_DRIVER
fields.description: Specifies the scheduler that deals with the volume operations.

fields.name: SWIFT_DEVICES
fields.description: List of labels to be used for creating disks for the VPX node

fields.name: SWIFT_DISK_SIZE_GB
fields.description: The size of the disk to be attached to an Storage Object Worker

fields.name: SWIFT_HASH_PATH_SUFFIX
fields.description: The hash path suffix for swift

fields.name: SWIFT_NODES_IPS
fields.description: The list of IP addresses of swift oject servers

fields.name: SWIFT_PROXY_ADDRESS
fields.description: The FQDN of the Object Storage API node

fields.name: TARGET_HOST
fields.description: 'iscsi' backend only: the FQDN of the iscsi target host exposed by OpenStack Nova Volume

fields.name: TARGET_PORT
fields.description: The port for the iSCSI protocol

fields.name: VMWAREAPI_WSDL_LOC
fields.description: The URL for the WSDL file for the VMWare Web Service API

fields.name: VOLUME_DISK_SIZE_GB
fields.description: 'iscsi' backend only: the size of the disk to be used for providing block storage volumes

fields.name: VOLUME_DRIVER
fields.description: The driver for the OpenStack Nova Volume Server

fields.name: VPX_ABSENT_FILES
fields.description: List of init files that must not be present (or removed) from the VPX node. To be used as node override with onetime=True only

fields.name: VPX_DESCRIPTION
fields.description: Brief description of the VPX node

fields.name: VPX_LABEL_PREFIX
fields.description: A prefix to be added to the VPX friendly name

fields.name: VPX_LOGGING_COLLECTOR
fields.description: The logging destination for syslog.

fields.name: VPX_LOGGING_LEVEL
fields.description: The syslog log level.

fields.name: VPX_RESTART_SERVICES
fields.description: List of services that need to be restarted on the node VPX. To be used as node override with onetime=True only
